data.title: Junior's Red
data.meta_description: Becky Fos' "Junior Red" presents a bright blue background with a highly defined redfish at the center. Her impasto technique and vivid strokes create an energetic and bold creation depicting one of Louisiana's most colorful catches.
data.text:
Mini Paper Prints are high-quality paper prints on satin-finished photo paper and include a half-inch white border on all sides of the image. Mini Paper Prints are not artist signed, nor numbered. Framing not included.

(Processing time between 1-2 weeks)

Large and Extra Large Paper Prints are high-quality paper prints on stark-white, heavyweight archival paper and include a 1-inch white border on all sides of the image. Large Paper Prints are artist signed and numbered out of a limited edition series of 100. Framing not included.

(Processing time between 1-2 weeks)

Canvas Prints are high-quality reproduction prints on stretched canvas. Canvas is stretch over 1.4-inch wooden stretcher bars and gallery wrap finished.

Canvas prints vary in size. All canvas prints are artist signed, and numbered out of a limited edition series of 50.

Canvas Prints are wired for hanging.

(Processing time between 3-6 weeks)

Embellished Canvas Prints: All Canvas Prints are eligible, for a fee, to receive embellishing. Select "Embellish Canvas" before adding desired canvas to cart. Using her palette knife, Becky Fos can hand-embellish the canvas print by applying a high-gloss varnish over the canvas print artwork. The application of varnish mimics the impasto texture of her original paintings.

(Processing time additional 7 days)
